{"word":"G3576 - νωθρός - nōthrós - no-thros' - Dull","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νωθρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nōthrós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">no-thros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dull</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மந்தமுள்ள, அசதியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"dull, slothful, lazy, sluggish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3541 - νόθος - nóthos - noth'-os/3541\">G3541</a>; <i>sluggish</i>, that is, (literally) <i>lazy</i>, or (figuratively) <i>stupid:</i> - dull, slothful.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}